== Salad

=== Into
Salad is a simple application that allow users to manage their projects & their feature, inspired by Cucumber, Salad allows you to create projects and associate features with them.

== Features
Manage projects & features
Create stories for features
Export features
Manage a stories steps

== Future features
In future releases, users will be able to link these features with LightHouse milestones & export features into Cucumber features & steps.

== Installation

Download
cd to directory
run scription/server
point browser to http://localhost:3000/projects